data.content:
Danh từ
(số nhiều, từ Mỹ blinders)
miếng da che mắt (ngựa không cho nhìn ngang)

noun
plural -ers
[count] US informal :a light on a car, truck, etc., that goes off and on and that is used as a warning or as a signal that the vehicle will be turning
Use your blinker [=indicator, (US) turn signal] when you turn.
blinkers [plural] chiefly Brit :leather pieces that are placed on either side of a horse's head next to its eyes :blinders
